        <obo:namespace>topic</obo:namespace>
        <oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>Protein secondary</oboInOwl:hasExactSynonym>
        <oboInOwl:hasDefinition>Topic concerning primarily the classification of proteins (from sequence or structural data) into clusters, groups, families etc., curation of a particular protein or protein family, or any other proteins that have been classified as members of a common group.</oboInOwl:hasDefinition>
